a> star Nolan North to be inducted into the “exclusive” club of PlayStation adventurers. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="PS5日期揭示-Indiana Jones和The Great Circle" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0VdnmreE1X0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Pre-orders for the PlayStation version of <em>The Great Circle</em> are <a href="https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/product/UP1003-PPSA26786_00-INDIANAJONESATGC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">now live</a> .</p><p> Released at the end of last year for Xbox and PC, <em>The Great Circle</em> was a surprise hit with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indiana-jones-more-games-the-great-circle-success-3821192">LucasFilm, who said they were now “super interested” in more Indiana Jones games</a> following its success.</p><p> Developers are currently working on a DLC called <em>The Order Of The Giants</em> , which will reportedly expand the early story of the main game and release at some point in 2025.</p><p> Set between the events of <em>Raiders Of The Lost Ark</em> and <em>The Last Crusade,</em> The Great Circle uses Harrison Ford&#39;s likeness but Indy was voiced by video game veteran Troy Baker for the project.</p><p> “There&#39;s so much history going into this. There&#39;s so much expectation,” <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/indiana-jones-great-circle-voice-actor-troy-baker-3818632">he told <em>NME</em></a> . “I had to unburden myself from that pretty quickly. If I had stayed underneath the weight of that legacy, I&#39;d never have been able to do it.” </p><figure id="attachment_3818638" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3818638" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3818638" src="https://